{"tid":780500,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[極多圖] 原來TWICE 周支瑜老母咁犀利","createTime":"2018-08-15T07:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T21:07:11.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa7604f1b739413076f8625d9a4c66e7dcb7f11","tid":780500,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:55:33.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE的19歲台灣成員周子瑜，以甜美長相受到歌迷喜愛，美貌更成為南韓女生的整形範本。<span style=\"color: red;\">她的媽媽黃燕玲是台南知名醫美診所院長，被問到是否有人拿著子瑜的照片進廠維修，子瑜媽媽自豪的說：「她就是我生的啊，我就是美的範本！」更大方承認自已對醫美「已經中毒」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/d3486637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2Fd3486637.jpg&h=c2d36553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜媽媽黃燕玲，以醫美診所院長身份出席活動。（圖／記者黃軍瑋攝）<br />\n<br />\n黃燕玲15日以醫美診所院長的身份，赴台北出席美容業大型活動，對於女兒周子瑜此次回台席程低調的說：「新聞都講得很清楚了，我再講的話人家覺得我炒新聞。」但講到醫美話匣子就關不上。她笑說：「我最喜歡客人問我醫美的問題，因為我臉上什麼都做過，你問哪一項我都有做過，知道什麼人適合什麼。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/d3486661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2Fd3486661.jpg&h=4e2b299b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜與媽媽黃燕玲合照有如姐妹。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">她大方承認自己從脈衝光、肉毒桿菌再打到玻尿酸，從額頭打到嘴唇，通通都嘗試過</span>，笑說：「打在嘴巴，有嘟嘟的感覺」。黃燕玲坦言：「有年紀了，必須要侵入式的美容，才會有效。」<br />\n<br />\n黃燕玲笑說自己前兩天才補打了玻尿酸，更鼓勵記者：「微整就是慢慢調，年輕就開始做，以後就不用動刀了。」從事醫美事業不免得親自體驗，但黃燕玲豪氣地說：<span style=\"color: red;\">「我經常覺得不夠滿意，因為我已經（對醫美）中毒了。」<br />\n</span><br />\n不過青春洋溢的子瑜保證是純天然，尤其招牌的「W溝下巴」更讓黃燕玲驕傲表示：「那是媽媽生得好。」也笑說：「到我診所不用拿子瑜的照片啦，問媽媽比較快！」聽到子瑜的下巴是不少女生的整形範本，黃燕玲也用專業口吻表示：「台灣的技術就做得很好了，不用去韓國！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/d3486642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2Fd3486642.jpg&h=ee5206fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲<span style=\"color: red;\">黃燕玲掛保證，子瑜的美貌是純天然「媽媽生得好」</span>。（圖／翻攝自臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岳母真係幾令女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cfe09700d541b0fd5ce8443c5d1daa02581842","tid":780500,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ff96c73a30a5d44de0fa45eba15ddfcdc8de0e","tid":780500,"uid":54927,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"廟街150"},{"pid":"965ee52c2071d414a41577f37f895bac55d2c9bd","tid":780500,"uid":177639,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"JYP又慳返舊錢"},{"pid":"4bdc45e8d0b7e02f73183a36a8c7294746ded0f8","tid":780500,"uid":76098,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"52ff96c73a30a5d44de0fa45eba15ddfcdc8de0e","tid":780500,"uid":54927,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"廟街150"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"150可以奶子瑜出世既地方 抵到爛"},{"pid":"588d230a04777a6a784bec0f75ff52b24900bc4b","tid":780500,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T08:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e6a9505d52001128e134412bc1d613ec03e701","tid":780500,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bdc45e8d0b7e02f73183a36a8c7294746ded0f8","tid":780500,"uid":76098,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"52ff96c73a30a5d44de0fa45eba15ddfcdc8de0e","tid":780500,"uid":54927,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"廟街150"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"150可以奶子瑜出世既地方 抵到爛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T08:06:38.000Z","msg":"又幾襟計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc508c39f4d4154fedef5f06c494bd908b3971e","tid":780500,"uid":29702,"like